RQ2: Pre-registration anonymous traces

Here we review the pre-registration traces of volunteers who we were able to link anonymous traces to their user accounts. There are 1571 volunteers who contributed anonymously before registering for an account. On average there were 9.41 and a standard deviation of 14.17 events, including classifying. Removing classifying events there were on average 0.49 and a standard deviation of 1.7 events.
